<item>
            <title>[LU-7573] rmmod command is missing the -w option</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-7573</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The rmmod command in the most recent linux versions we support has no -w option.  Since some of our tests use this option those tests fail.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Currently the only linux versions impacted by this problem are RHEL 7.2 and SLES 12.  Over time there will likely be more.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="33743">LU-7573</key>
