Branch: master&lt;br/&gt;
Current Patch Set: 1&lt;br/&gt;
Commit: 086e935f063292c6b356e8218de406ce37172bb2&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="136706" author="bogl" created="Thu, 17 Dec 2015 15:37:26 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The only test known to hit this problem for sure is sanity, test 60a.  The script run-llog.sh called by this test uses &apos;rmmod -vw&apos;.  There may be others not detected yet.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Until a better fix is developed to avoid the use of the missing option I will work up a patch to just skip the test in cases where there is no -w option available.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
